title: Preseason WK 1 recap & NFC North preview
itunes:title: Preseason WK 1 recap & NFC North preview
description:
A room filled with heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler – discuss the latest NFL news, including Eagles quarterback Carson Wentz suffering a hairline rib fracture and Saints rookie Sheldon Rankins breaking his fibula during practice. Then the heroes recap the first week of the preseason before wrapping the podcast with a preview of the NFC North.
